item.title: MariaDB Can't Create Test File
item.description: Sep 19 11:54:47 bung systemd[1]: Starting MariaDB 10.3.36 database server... Sep 19 11:54:48 bung mysqld[14684]: 2022-09-19 11:54:48 0 [Note] /usr/sbin/mysqld (mysqld 10.3.36-MariaDB-0+deb10u1) starting as process 14684 ... Sep 19 11:54:48 bung mysqld[14684]: 2022-09-19 11:54:48 0 [Warning] Can't create test file /var/lib/mysql/bung.lower-test Sep 19 11:54:48 bung mysqld[14684]: [90B blob data] Sep 19 11:54:48 bung mysqld[14684]: 2022-09-19 11:54:48 0 [ERROR] Aborting Sep 19 11:54:48 bung systemd[1]: mariadb.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=1/FAILURE Sep 19 11:54:48 bung systemd[1]: mariadb.
